snippet.title: Completely Stretchy | Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Grombi Isles! Completely Stretchy is coming to Steam on December 12th, wishlist now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1587570?snr=5000_5100__

A befuddling mishap has made you COMPLETELY STRETCHY! Stretch, swing and stick around the delightfully odd and vibrant Grombi Isles in this eccentric and light-hearted 3D platformer.
